org.sbml.jsbml.ext.fbc

Class FBCModelPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.AbstractTreeNode
      • org.sbml.jsbml.ext.AbstractSBasePlugin
        • org.sbml.jsbml.ext.fbc.AbstractFBCSBasePlugin
          • org.sbml.jsbml.ext.fbc.FBCModelPlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, TreeNode, SBasePlugin, TreeNodeWithChangeSupport

    public class FBCModelPlugin
extends AbstractFBCSBasePlugin
    FBCModelPlugin is the extended Model class for the FBC package.

    It is extended by the addition of two children, list of FluxBound and list of Objective

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Nicolas Rodriguez

        public void setActiveObjective(String activeObjective)

      • setListOfObjectives

        public void setListOfObjectives(ListOf<Objective> listOfObjectives)
        Sets the given ListOf<Objective>.

        If the given list is an instance of ListOfObjectives, a call of this method is identical to directly calling setListOfObjectives(ListOfObjectives). Otherwise, a new ListOfObjectives will be created from the given ListOf.

        Note that in the second case there is no active objective defined.

        Parameters:
        listOfObjectives -
